  <%= form_tag import_items_path, multipart: true do %>
    <p>To convert the existing serial register delete the customer column then convert to .csv and replace the header row with<br>
      <font size ="1">serial_number,job_id,engine,engine_type,engine_serial,alternator,alternator_type,alternator_serial,detail,status_detail,gesan_number,ppsr</font>
